data.title: Paris Eternal HyP and BenBest Play Soccer: Access Granted
data.description: Malik Forté picks up HyP and BenBest from the Paris Eternal for an afternoon of soccer. Hear about how the team is overcoming the language barriers, adjusting to life in LA, and how they deal with the pressure of playing on the big stage in this episode of Access Granted presented by Toyota.

data.title: Overwatch League MVP Pro-Files: Twilight
data.description: In this Overwatch League MVP Pro-File we're taking a look at the Vancouver Titans' Flex Support Twilight. Originally overshadowed by the likes of JJoNak and ryujehong, Twilight had a breakout year dominating the competition with his Zenyatta play. His consistent healing combined with his insane damage dealing easily makes Twilight a contender for this year's MVP. Cast your vote now for this year’s MVP on twitter using #OWLMVP plus your favorite player’s BattleTag. Now is your chance to be a part of history: vote for the Overwatch League MVP presented by T-Mobile.

data.title: Flying Ace: London’s Championship Skin
data.description: As the Grand Finals champions of the inaugural season of the Overwatch League, the London Spitfire head down to Blizzard headquarters to be the first to lay eyes on the skin developed to celebrate their historic victory.
